Please refer to the SmugNDrag mercurial repository for exhaustive change details.

SmugNDrag ChangeLog
===================

Changes in v1.5 (2008-09-02):
  * added the ability to paste the description
  * only add the alt attribute if the description field is populated

Changes in v1.4 (2008-06-16):
  * fixed UI issues
  * added Sparkle framework for automatic updating
  * added Preferences panel for Sparkle

Changes in v1.3 (2008-06-08):
  * added SmugMug destination options
